{"tid":888912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(CCTVB注意) 多間大學設彈性收生政策 教局指資助大學收生有自主權","createTime":"2018-11-04T07:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T12:50:32.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea5b8a636dc086eeb3c7ec4d1c7976278c6b748","tid":888912,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:12:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5bdd7912e60383ab0ee7c263?fbclid=IwAR3iOzWclEVtNyISJpUR8wJsdkJvzc2S_0n0E3YM3rnXe88aoA0rFZJHZ0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5bdd7912e60383ab0ee7c263%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3iOzWclEVtNyISJpUR8wJsdkJvzc2S_0n0E3YM3rnXe88aoA0rFZJHZ0I&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=525628c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5bdd7912e60383ab0ee7c263?fbclid=IwAR3iOzWclEVtNyISJpUR8wJsdkJvzc2S_0n0E3YM3rnXe88aoA0rFZJHZ0I</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學採用新計分制，取錄下學年入讀的學士課程學生，在文憑試考獲5級或以上，會額外加分。教育局回應指，資助大學收生享有自主權。<br />\n<br />\n除了港大，部分大學亦公布明年的彈性收生政策。中文大學方面，下學年報讀理學院、工程學院的學生，如在文憑試三個STEM類選修科，例如物理和化學等取得三粒*，即使在四個核心科未能達到最低要求「3322」，會酌情考慮。<br />\n<br />\n理大表示，若學生未達最低要求，但在四個核心科及兩個選修科取得三科5**或以上，或會酌情處理。<br />\n<br />\n科大對於文憑試成績低於最低門檻一個級別，但最佳五科成績中奪得5粒*，亦會酌情考慮。<br />\n=============================<br />\n我最期待的畫面出現了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb903b19d4a1ced4750b57b5010056c81b93f87","tid":888912,"uid":159518,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"走返A-level條路，變相摑政府一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744dce5f31c551d99ff485ff8cff65aca5c35675","tid":888912,"uid":1524,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"明顯奶晒野啦，Engine 寧願收一個物理有5* 或以上都唔收一個全4啦"},{"pid":"010587bd6348dad877ea417521417d654d95c851","tid":888912,"uid":15325